frameDefinitions: An Asset, the safety of which is desirable, is protected from damage by a covering, the Armor.
A particular Situation is likely (or unlikely) to result in a harmful event befalling an Asset.
A Terrorist commits a violent or otherwise harmful Act upon a Victim in order to coerce or terrorize a government or populace.
A Shopper looks for Goods in order to purchase them.
This frame refers to clothing and its characteristics,  including anything that people conventionally wear.
Money is a medium used for exchanging goods and services.
frameExamples: They were wearing nothing but primitive wooden <t><fex name='Armor'>armor</fex></t>.
Their <t>terrorism</t> against civilians will not be tolerated.
Claudia dressed in a dark green cotton <t>DRESS</t> clasped round her slender waist with a broad yellow belt , drank a cup of coffee and opened her neglected post .
The <t>money</t> for our daughter's college education is currently earning interest in a savings account.
listRoleDefinitions: The <fen>Armor</fen> prevents the <fen>Asset</fen> from coming to harm.
An object or situation that could damage the <fen>Asset</fen>.
Something desirable which might be lost or damaged and which is protected by <fen>Armor</fen>.
The <fen>Situation</fen> which may lead to a harmful event.
Something judged to be desirable or valuable which might be lost or damaged.
A concrete or abstract entity which may come to cause the loss of, or damage to the Asset.
The time period during which the <fen>Situation</fen> has the specified level of safety.
A particular location for which the <fen>Situation</fen> is safe. Frequently, it is to be inferred that the characteristics of the location make various <fen>Situation</fen>s safe or unsafe.
The <fen>Terrorist</fen> commits the <fen>Act</fen> of terror for political or ideological gains.
The <fen>Act</fen> is the harmful action performed by the <fen>Terrorist</fen> or terrorist organization.
The <fen>Victim</fen> is most directly affected or harmed by the <fen>Act</fen> of terrorism.
The location in time when the <fen>Act</fen> takes place.
The location where the <fen>Act</fen> takes place.
The person who attempts to find the <fen>Goods</fen>.
This is the entity that the Ground may contain. Typically, it is expressed as a<ment>for</ment>-PP.
This role identifies the time when the shopping occurs.
A spatial setting larger than the Ground in which the Shopping event occurs.
This role identifes the clothing worn.
<fen>Money</fen> is used as a medium of exchange.
listRoleExamples: Metal <fex>armor</fex> was so heavy that sometimes knights found it difficult to move.
The <fex>anti-mine</fex> armor being developed by the army is still months from completion.
Our company's <fex>tank</fex> armor provides an unprecedented about of protection.
Most people agree, <fex>going over 100mph</fex> is unsafe.
Several domestic <fex>terrorists</fex> were operating from the site during the mid 1990s.
Many have suffered due to their acts of <fex><t>terrorism</t></fex>.
Cowardly acts of terrorism <fex>upon innocent men, women, and children</fex> is not a doorway to Heaven, but a gateway to Hell.
The children were shopping for gifts for their parents <fex>before Christmas</fex>.
